cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE

The paper deals with natural language processing and reasoning, which suggests that it belongs to the category of Computation and Language (cs.CL). The use of neural networks and logic programming also indicates that it could be classified under Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval and search, which could place it under Information Retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the use of similarity functions and fine-tuning of representations suggests that it could be classified under Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE).
